data.description: Looking to for a starter home or to downsize?  This 3-bedroom ranch could be it.   This home has an open concept with cathedral ceilings.  Located in an established neighborhood which is walking distance to playground, shops, and the home of the ''Sanford Mainers''.  Showings start Saturday May 27th.  All offers due Tuesday at 5pm with a 24-hour response time.
